show.title: Cleopatra
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://applinks.kukufm.com/oVix7FfFrr1hyVuG8
show.description: When a young woman finds herself trapped under her domineering stepfather's control, survival becomes her daily battle. Despite the suffocating circumstances, Cleopatra's fierce spirit refuses to be extinguished. As she endures one crushing setback after another, a flicker of hope keeps her going—the dream that someday she'll break free from the chains that bind her and build a future on her own terms. In this riveting tale of resilience and determination, witness how far one woman will go to claim her freedom and rewrite her destiny.
